card.text:
Ward {1}
At the beginning of each end step, if a land card was put into a graveyard from anywhere this turn, put a +1/+1 counter on Ku'I. Then if Ku'I has four or more +1/+1 counters on it, create a 1/1 green Elemental Rabbit creature token.
Partner (You can have two commanders if both have partner.)

